Why ZeRO-2 instead of ZeRO-3 here: This is the regular train_lvr.py (no prototype), 3B model on 2×46 GB. ZeRO-2 shards only optimizer states — each GPU keeps the full model, so forward/backward never needs to gather params across GPUs. Much lower communication overhead for 2-GPU setup.

